---
---

<section class="newsletter-section">
  <div class="container newsletter-panel reveal">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Newsletter</p>
      <h2>每周收到一封睡前历史信</h2>
      <p>像新产品发布订阅页一样简洁。先收集真正愿意持续回来的人，再接 Mailchimp、ConvertKit、Beehiiv 或自建会员系统。</p>
    </div>
    <form class="newsletter-form" action="#" method="post">
      <label>
        <span>邮箱</span>
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="name@email.com" autocomplete="email" />
      </label>
      <button type="submit">加入名单</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>
